      "writtenOn": "2016-11-30T18:49:43Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Is this only for testing? It sounds like at the moment it\u0027s only for a very specific case. Maybe this should be behind a flag?\n\nOn another note, this exclusive with SkColorSpace. Would it make sense to have some dummy color space that means unsupported ICC? (Again, maybe only behind some flag?)",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 788,
        "startChar": 17,
        "endLine": 788,
        "endChar": 31
      },
      "revId": "8e001806c26d6bca5ffbc07e6af17847c4621b83",
